---
title: Creamy Italian Sausage Rigatoni with Mushrooms, Tomatoes and Spinach
description: This decadently creamy rigatoni is packed full of savoury Italian sausage, juicy tomatoes, spinach and earthy mushrooms. One bite will have you saying, "that's amore!"

